# Frontend Testing Rules (Extension)

## 1. UI Behavior Focus
- Tests must validate user-visible behavior
- Do not test internal state directly

## 2. Mocking Rule
- All services must be mocked in unit tests
- External API calls must never be real

## 3. Rendering Focus
- Prefer interaction-based assertions
- Validate what the user sees and does

## 4. Library Consistency
- Use a single frontend testing framework consistently